{"tid":2215180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣祁家威列時代雜誌百大人物 盼跨國同性婚姻速合法","createTime":"2020-09-23T21:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T22:49:24.000Z","uid":337052,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fcbbc2d02368c7bf91104b13763033ef6e52d0b2","tid":2215180,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T21:24:23.000Z","msg":"祁家威列時代雜誌百大人物 盼跨國同性婚姻速合法<br />\n最新更新：2020/09/23 13:04<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200923/2000x1125_0082013131550.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200923%2F2000x1125_0082013131550.jpg&h=067b74b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">時代雜誌公布年度百大最具影響力人物（TIME100）名單，台灣除了總統蔡英文入選外，同志運動先驅祁家威（圖）也獲選。（中央社檔案照片）</span><br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者吳欣紜台北23日電）同志運動先驅祁家威名列「時代雜誌」編輯評選的年度百大最具影響力人物名單，祁家威今天受訪原以為是詐騙，之後開心表示，獲選就是肯定，期待跨國同性婚姻可以儘速合法。<br />\n<br />\n時代雜誌（TIME）公布編輯評選的年度百大最具影響力人物（TIME100）完整名單，除了總統蔡英文入選外，祁家威也獲選。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009230109.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202009230109.aspx&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=3426cb9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202009230109.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"6ad595d65b7e7966deda14a53e022f19f36379a9","tid":2215180,"uid":177955,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T22:49:24.000Z","msg":"恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}